{"title":"Bootstrap","uid":"b3291068b1bc15312c82013b6dd7412c","slug":"Bootstrap4","date":"2021-04-07T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Bootstrap4.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.5/getting-started/introduction/\">Bootstrap官網</a></p>\n<p>以下是選單翻譯：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Getting started 快速開始</li>\n<li>Layout 排版</li>\n<li>Content 內容</li>\n<li>Components 元件</li>\n<li>Utilities 通用類別</li>\n<li>Extend 擴增</li>\n<li>Migration 更版紀錄</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"起手式，放入-Css-amp-Js-CDN\"><a href=\"#起手式，放入-Css-amp-Js-CDN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"起手式，放入( Css &amp; Js ) CDN\"></a>起手式，放入( Css &amp; Js ) CDN</h3><ul>\n<li>Css:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;bootstrap@4.5.3&#x2F;dist&#x2F;css&#x2F;bootstrap.min.css&quot; integrity&#x3D;&quot;sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e&#x2F;ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2&quot; crossorigin&#x3D;&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Js:</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;code.jquery.com&#x2F;jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js&quot; integrity&#x3D;&quot;sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj&#x2F;zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj&quot; crossorigin&#x3D;&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;\n&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;popper.js@1.16.1&#x2F;dist&#x2F;umd&#x2F;popper.min.js&quot; integrity&#x3D;&quot;sha384-9&#x2F;reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN&quot; crossorigin&#x3D;&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;\n&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;npm&#x2F;bootstrap@4.5.3&#x2F;dist&#x2F;js&#x2F;bootstrap.min.js&quot; integrity&#x3D;&quot;sha384-w1Q4orYjBQndcko6MimVbzY0tgp4pWB4lZ7lr30WKz0vr&#x2F;aWKhXdBNmNb5D92v7s&quot; crossorigin&#x3D;&quot;anonymous&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"語意化標題\"><a href=\"#語意化標題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"語意化標題\"></a>語意化標題</h3><ol>\n<li><code>&lt;s&gt;</code> 刪除線在文字上</li>\n<li><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> 文字下底線</li>\n<li><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> 極小文字</li>\n<li><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code> 粗體</li>\n<li><code>&lt;b&gt;</code> 突出顯示、而不增加重要性</li>\n<li><code>&lt;i&gt;</code> 語音、技術用語</li>\n<li><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> 行內元素，沒有任何語意</li>\n<li><code>&lt;em&gt;</code> 文字斜體</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"常用切版\"><a href=\"#常用切版\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用切版\"></a>常用切版</h2><h3 id=\"1-常見-list-清單\"><a href=\"#1-常見-list-清單\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 常見 list 清單\"></a>1. 常見 list 清單</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;ul class&#x3D;&quot;list-unstyled&quot;&gt; \n&lt;!-- 此 class語意為清除 ul 格式 --&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Consectetur adipiscing elit&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Integer molestie lorem at massa&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Facilisis in pretium nisl aliquet&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Nulla volutpat aliquam velit\n    &lt;ul&gt;\n      &lt;li&gt;Phasellus iaculis neque&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n      &lt;li&gt;Purus sodales ultricies&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n      &lt;li&gt;Vestibulum laoreet porttitor sem&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n      &lt;li&gt;Ac tristique libero volutpat at&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Faucibus porta lacus fringilla vel&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Aenean sit amet erat nunc&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n  &lt;li&gt;Eget porttitor lorem&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"2-描述清單\"><a href=\"#2-描述清單\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 描述清單\"></a>2. 描述清單</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlmixed\" data-language=\"htmlmixed\"><code class=\"language-htmlmixed\">&lt;dl class&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3&quot;&gt;Description lists&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n  &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-9&quot;&gt;A description list is perfect for defining terms.&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n\n  &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3&quot;&gt;Euismod&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n  &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-9&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper eget lacinia odio sem nec elit.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n\n  &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3&quot;&gt;Malesuada porta&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n  &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-9&quot;&gt;Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod.&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n\n  &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 text-truncate&quot;&gt;Truncated term is truncated&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n&lt;!--此class 意思為 dt 標題超出邊框的字體會自動隱藏  --&gt;\n  &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-9&quot;&gt;Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus.&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n\n  &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3&quot;&gt;Nesting&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n  &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-9&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;dl class&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;dt class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-4&quot;&gt;Nested definition list&lt;&#x2F;dt&gt;\n      &lt;dd class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-8&quot;&gt;Aenean posuere, tortor sed cursus feugiat, nunc augue blandit nunc.&lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;dl&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;dd&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;dl&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Image\"><a href=\"#Image\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Image\"></a>Image</h2><h3 id=\"1-圖片自適應縮放-img-fluid\"><a href=\"#1-圖片自適應縮放-img-fluid\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 圖片自適應縮放 (img-fluid)\"></a>1. 圖片自適應縮放 (img-fluid)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;img-fluid&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Responsive image&quot;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>img-fluid</code> :<br>    會自動設定 max-width:100% 以及     height:auto<br>圖片不管大小都要加上<br>圖片過大的話就加上 width:?px 讓他小一點即可</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"2-頭像效果-thumbnail-（圖片四周留白邊）\"><a href=\"#2-頭像效果-thumbnail-（圖片四周留白邊）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 頭像效果(thumbnail)（圖片四周留白邊）\"></a>2. 頭像效果(thumbnail)（圖片四周留白邊）</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlmixed\" data-language=\"htmlmixed\"><code class=\"language-htmlmixed\">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;img-thumbnail&quot;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-圓角效果-rounded\"><a href=\"#3-圓角效果-rounded\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 圓角效果(rounded)\"></a>3. 圓角效果(rounded)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;rounded float-left&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;...&quot;&gt;\n&lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;rounded float-right&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;...&quot;&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"很重要\"><a href=\"#很重要\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"很重要(!)\"></a>很重要(!)</h4><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>上方圓角效果使用 float 去做排版，<br>因此連續使用的話，<br>必須得在父層加上清除浮動 class&#x3D;”clear-fix”，版面才會正常</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-置中做法-超常用！\"><a href=\"#4-置中做法-超常用！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 置中做法(超常用！)\"></a>4. 置中做法(超常用！)</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;text-center&quot;&gt;\n&lt;!-- 文字置中 --&gt;\n  &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;img-fluid mx-auto d-block&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;...&quot;&gt;\n&lt;!-- 1.自適應大小 2.margin right&amp;left :auto 3.display:block   --&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"5-圖片描述-figure\"><a href=\"#5-圖片描述-figure\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 圖片描述 (figure)\"></a>5. 圖片描述 (figure)</h2><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mfwTWf3.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>外層使用 figure class名稱<br><code>&lt;fitcaption&gt;</code>:圖片描述</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;figure class&#x3D;&quot;figure&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;...&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;figure-img img-fluid rounded&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;...&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;figcaption class&#x3D;&quot;figure-caption&quot;&gt;A caption for the above image.&lt;&#x2F;figcaption&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;figure&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-Table\"><a href=\"#6-Table\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6. Table\"></a>6. Table</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.5/content/tables/\">更多Table資料</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>表格架構:<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0pZdRP1.png\" alt=\"image\"><br>範例：<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ziJdHYM.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlmixed\" data-language=\"htmlmixed\"><code class=\"language-htmlmixed\">&lt;table class&#x3D;&quot;table&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;thead&gt;\n    &lt;tr&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;col&quot;&gt;#&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;col&quot;&gt;First&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;col&quot;&gt;Last&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;col&quot;&gt;Handle&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;thead&gt;\n  &lt;tbody&gt;\n    &lt;tr&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;Mark&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;Otto&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;@mdo&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;\n    &lt;tr&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;2&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;Jacob&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;Thornton&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;@fat&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;\n    &lt;tr&gt;\n      &lt;th scope&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;3&lt;&#x2F;th&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;Larry&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;the Bird&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n      &lt;td&gt;@twitter&lt;&#x2F;td&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;tr&gt;\n  &lt;&#x2F;tbody&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;table&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>滾動卷軸(table-responsive)</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;table-responsive&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;table class&#x3D;&quot;table&quot;&gt;\n    ...\n  &lt;&#x2F;table&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>超大裝置:<code>&lt;div class=&quot;table-responsive-xl&quot;&gt;</code><br>大裝置:<code>&lt;div class=&quot;table-responsive-lg&quot;&gt;</code><br>中裝置:<code>&lt;div class=&quot;table-responsive-md&quot;&gt;</code><br>小裝置:<code>&lt;div class=&quot;table-responsive-sm&quot;&gt;</code></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Grid-網格\"><a href=\"#Grid-網格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Grid 網格\"></a>Grid 網格</h2><p>Width:960px<br>分成12 直欄位</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>以下範例：<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9aGIAay.png\" alt=\"image\"></p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\">column Width:60px\nGutter Width:20px\nGutter on outside:10px</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"重點-！\"><a href=\"#重點-！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"重點(！)\"></a>重點(！)</h3><h4 id=\"1-class-x3D-”col-xx”-外層是-class-x3D-”row”\"><a href=\"#1-class-x3D-”col-xx”-外層是-class-x3D-”row”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. class&#x3D;”col-xx” 外層是 class&#x3D;”row”\"></a>1. class&#x3D;”col-xx” 外層是 class&#x3D;”row”</h4><h4 id=\"2-class-x3D-”row”-裡面是-class-x3D-”col-xx”\"><a href=\"#2-class-x3D-”row”-裡面是-class-x3D-”col-xx”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. class&#x3D;”row” 裡面是 class&#x3D;”col-xx”\"></a>2. class&#x3D;”row” 裡面是 class&#x3D;”col-xx”</h4><h4 id=\"3-頁面內容請放在-class-x3D-”col-xx”-的內層\"><a href=\"#3-頁面內容請放在-class-x3D-”col-xx”-的內層\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.頁面內容請放在 class&#x3D;”col-xx” 的內層\"></a>3.頁面內容請放在 class&#x3D;”col-xx” 的內層</h4><h4 id=\"主要原因為空間補回以及-flex\"><a href=\"#主要原因為空間補回以及-flex\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主要原因為空間補回以及 flex\"></a>主要原因為空間補回以及 flex</h4><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/demobst4grid-forked-b32eg\">code 範例</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"RWD\"><a href=\"#RWD\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"RWD\"></a>RWD</h2><ol>\n<li>Extra small &lt;&#x3D;576px(col-*)</li>\n<li>Small 576~767px (col-sm-*)</li>\n<li>Medium 768~991px (col-md-*)</li>\n<li>Large 992~1199px (col-lg-*)</li>\n<li>Extra large ≥1200px (col-xl-*)</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"flex-屬性\"><a href=\"#flex-屬性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"flex 屬性\"></a>flex 屬性</h2><ol>\n<li>display flex</li>\n<li>flex-direction</li>\n<li>justify-content</li>\n<li>align-items</li>\n<li>flex-wrap</li>\n<li>align-content(限制 wrap)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>組合範例圖：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>外層屬性 (控制外層)<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PmuHzrU.png\" alt=\"截圖\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>內層屬性 (控制內層)<br><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cSfMu5E.png\" alt=\"截圖\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/demobst4gridrwd-b32eg?file=/index.html\">code 範例</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"補充\"><a href=\"#補充\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"補充\"></a>補充</h3><p>order(排列順序):</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-3 order-2&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;第二張圖&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-3 order-1&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;第一張圖&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-3 order-3&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;第三張圖&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>flex-wrap(換行):</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;d-flex flex-wrap bg-secondary&quot;&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;2&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;3&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;4&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;5&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;6&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n       &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;7&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>align-content(內元件統一對齊)</p>\n<p>&#x3D;&#x3D;重點:必須得要有 flex-wrap 才可以使用&#x3D;&#x3D;</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;d-flex flex-wrap align-content-center&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;height: 100vh&quot;&gt;\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 套上高度，方便觀看\n     &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;11231&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;2123&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;313&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n     &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm-3 box-auto&quot;&gt;313&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n   &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"container-主要是被用來定義最外層的容器\"><a href=\"#container-主要是被用來定義最外層的容器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"container(主要是被用來定義最外層的容器)\"></a>container(主要是被用來定義最外層的容器)</h2><p>使用上非為兩大類：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>container-fluid(滿版寬度)</li>\n<li>container-(階段固定寬度</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"margin-amp-padding-spacing-妙用！\"><a href=\"#margin-amp-padding-spacing-妙用！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"margin &amp; padding (spacing 妙用！)\"></a>margin &amp; padding (spacing 妙用！)</h2><p>語法：class &#x3D; {property  p or m }-{sides 方向}-{size 大小}</p>\n<ol>\n<li>property</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>m - for classes that set margin</li>\n<li>p - for classes that set padding</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>sides</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>t - for classes that set margin-top or padding-top</li>\n<li>b - for classes that set margin-bottom or padding-bottom</li>\n<li>s - for classes that set margin-left or padding-left in LTR, margin-right or padding-right in RTL</li>\n<li>e - for classes that set margin-right or padding-right in LTR,margin-left or padding-left in RTL</li>\n<li>x - for classes that set both *-left and *-right</li>\n<li>y - for classes that set both *-top and *-bottom blank - for classes that set a margin or padding on all 4 sides of the element</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>sizes</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>0 - for classes that eliminate the margin or padding by setting it to 0</li>\n<li>1 - (by default) for classes that set the margin or padding to $spacer * .25</li>\n<li>2 - (by default) for classes that set the margin or padding to $spacer * .5</li>\n<li>3 - (by default) for classes that set the margin or padding to $spacer</li>\n<li>4 - (by default) for classes that set the margin or padding to $spacer * 1.5</li>\n<li>5 - (by default) for classes that set the margin or padding to $spacer * 3</li>\n<li>auto - for classes that set the margin to auto (You can add more sizes by adding entries to the $spacers Sass map variable.)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>語法簡寫:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">.mt-0 &#123; \n  margin-top: 0 !important;\n&#125;\n\n.ms-1 &#123;        &#x2F;&#x2F; 一個 spacer &#x3D; 1rem(16px)\n  margin-left: ($spacer * .25) (16px * 0.25);\n&#125;\n\n.px-2 &#123;        &#x2F;&#x2F; x &#x3D; left &amp; right\n  padding-left: ($spacer * .5) !important;\n  padding-right: ($spacer * .5) !important;\n&#125;\n\n.py-2 &#123;        &#x2F;&#x2F; x &#x3D; top &amp; bottom\n  padding-top: ($spacer * .5) !important;\n  padding-bottom: ($spacer * .5) !important;\n&#125;\n\n.p-3 &#123;        \n  padding: $spacer !important;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p>實作範例：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;!-- 使用m-0 來去掉 p段落原始存在的 margin --&gt;\n&lt;!-- 使用 mt-2 來隔開兩個 box --&gt;\n&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box p-2&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;&quot;&gt;\n          Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi magni\n          ullam voluptas, nihil eum, reiciendis esse adipisci, necessitatibus\n          quidem culpa vel aut error repudiandae similique ea accusantium quia\n          unde dolorum.\n        &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n        &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;m-0&quot;&gt;\n          Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi magni\n          ullam voluptas, nihil eum, reiciendis esse adipisci, necessitatibus\n          quidem culpa vel aut error repudiandae similique ea accusantium quia\n          unde dolorum.\n        &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box p-2 mt-2&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;m-0&quot;&gt;\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quas vitae\n          rerum assumenda harum saepe minima sint omnis esse, aut fugit? Ab\n          voluptatem magnam quos veniam laudantium, enim rem nisi ipsam.\n        &lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n\n      &lt;!-- 第一個靠左，兩個靠右 --&gt;\n      &lt;!-- 先使用 justify-content-end --&gt;\n      &lt;!-- 藉由 margin auto 特性來推擠  --&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;row mt-2 justify-content-end&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-2&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;1&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-2 ml-auto&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;2&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-2&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box&quot;&gt;3&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n    &lt;!-- 置中用法 --&gt;\n      &lt;!-- 使用 mx-auto 加上固定寬度，來置中--&gt;\n      &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;box mx-auto p-1&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;width: 200px&quot;&gt;\n        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Ratione at in,\n        quidem fugit odio reiciendis quisquam id. Iste, nobis perspiciatis.\n      &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>實作範例：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/pen/JjRRLqY\">相簿排版</a></li>\n</ol>\n","text":"Bootstrap官網 以下是選單翻譯： Getting started 快速開始 Layout 排版 Content 內容 Components 元件 Utilities 通用類別 Extend 擴增 Migration 更版紀錄 起手式，放入( Css &amp; Js ) ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"13k","symbolsTime":"12 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"BootStrap","slug":"BootStrap","count":1,"path":"api/categories/BootStrap.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"BootStrap","slug":"BootStrap","count":1,"path":"api/tags/BootStrap.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B5%B7%E6%89%8B%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%BE%E5%85%A5-Css-amp-Js-CDN\"><span class=\"toc-text\">起手式，放入( Css &amp; Js ) CDN</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AA%9E%E6%84%8F%E5%8C%96%E6%A8%99%E9%A1%8C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">語意化標題</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%88%87%E7%89%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">常用切版</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"